Package de.lmu.ifi.dbs.elki.visualization.style.marker

Draw plot markers

See: Description


  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    MarkerLibrary
    A marker library is a class that can generate and draw various styles of markers.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CircleMarkers
    Simple marker library that just draws colored circles at the given coordinates.
    MinimalMarkers
    Simple marker library that just draws colored rectangles at the given coordinates.
    PrettyMarkers
    Marker library achieving a larger number of styles by combining different shapes with different colors.
